SQL_STMT_U.val: select PAIN_RUNNUMBER, min(PAIN_BANK_ADMNO), min(PAIN_FILE_LEDG_NO), min(PAIN_BANKFILETYPE), min(PAIN_SPLIT_URGENT), min(PAIN_HGRP_CODE), min(PAIN_CURRENCY), min(ADMN_NAME), min(BANK_NAME), COUNT(*) as COUNT, cast(sum(PAIN_AMOUNT) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/PAIN left outer join :1/ADMN on ADMN_NO = PAIN_BANK_ADMNO left outer join :1/BANK on BANK_ADMNO = PAIN_BANK_ADMNO and BANK_LEDG_NO = PAIN_FILE_LEDG_NO where PAIN_TRANSFERRED = 'N' and PAIN_LEDGERBOOKED = 'Y' and PAIN_APPROVED = 'Y' and PAIN_BANKFILETYPE > 0 and PAIN_ERRORCODE = 0 and PAIN_RUNNUMBER > 0 and (PAIN_BANKACCOUNTDEBTOR <> '' or PAIN_IBAN <> '') and PAIN_ACTIVEUSER = ':2' and PAIN_ADMNO_DEBTOR in (:3) and PAIN_HGRP_CODE in (:4) and :5 and PAIN_TYPE in (:6) group by PAIN_RUNNUMBER order by PAIN_RUNNUMBER for fetch only
